Out of abundance of caution to protect our users from an extremely rare security issue affecting a very small number of users we invalidated all authenticated sessions on GitHub.com. We encourage you to log back in. Learn more here
GitHub security update: A bug related to handling of authenticated sessions - The GitHub Blog
On the evening of March 8, we invalidated all authenticated sessions on GitHub.com created prior to 12:03 UTC on March 8 out of an abundance of caution.
